00:30:48,657 --> 00:30:50,242
- Nope, I can hear you.

574
00:30:50,284 --> 00:30:50,993
- Oh!

575
00:30:51,035 --> 00:30:52,369
He speaks too.

576
00:30:52,411 --> 00:30:54,038
- And you walk upright.

577
00:30:54,079 --> 00:30:55,080
Amazing.

578
00:30:55,122 --> 00:30:55,873
Evolution.

