Have you not seen
the news lately?

632
00:33:55,010 --> 00:33:56,178
- Okay, okay.

633
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:56,881
Stand up.

634
00:33:59,264 --> 00:34:00,891
Do me a favor,
get your hands up.

635
00:34:02,601 --> 00:34:04,728
You always have to
protect yourself.

636
00:34:04,770 --> 00:34:06,772
Chin down, hands up.

