780
00:41:10,278 --> 00:41:12,864
I'm still trying to wrap
my head around all of this.

781
00:41:12,906 --> 00:41:14,258
- [Maxine] You sure
you're an honor student?

782
00:41:14,282 --> 00:41:16,618
